# BILLING MODEL (Med Spa)

**Option A — Setup + monthly**  
Setup: $500–1,500 (one-time). Monthly: $300–800 per location.  
- Med spa ACV is lower than legal; volume (multi-location or many single locations) drives revenue.

**Option B — No setup, monthly only**  
Setup: $0. Monthly: $400–800 per location.  
- Easier yes; good for pilot and proof.

**Recommendation:**  
- Start at $300–500/mo per location for pilot; raise as you add proof (testimonials, ROI).  
- Multi-location deals at $800–1,500/mo total (2–3 locations) improve unit economics.

Stripe: Subscription required before Twilio activation. Cancel disables automation.

