# SECURITY & COMPLIANCE (Med Spa)

- Supabase RLS, encrypted credentials, JWT auth, rate limiting, webhook verification.
- Compliance: No medical or treatment advice. Call/SMS consent and opt-out (TCPA). Data handling: PII stored securely; no PHI beyond contact info and appointment context. One-pager for prospects: “Korvo handles intake and booking only; your staff handles all medical and treatment decisions.”

